These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, water, mirinda, fanta, 7up, almond-milk
The people have 6 different hobbies: magic-tricks, card-games, photography, sudoku, dancing, filmmaking
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice  | mirinda    | fanta  | water      | 7up    |
| Hobby      | card-games  | filmmaking | dancing | magic-tricks | sudoku | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: musical, horror, fantasy, scientific, thriller, zombie
6 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, chinchilla, rat, snake, hedgehog
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
6. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
9. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | thriller | horror | zombie | scientific     | fantasy  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | hamster    | turtle      | hedgehog  | rat | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, dubstep, jazz, ambient, funk
There are 6 different nationalities: russian, turkish, indian, brazilian, japanese, italian
1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the japanese##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the italian##1
6. the fan of ambient is on the left of the turkish##1
7. the brazilian is on the far right##1
8. the indian is the fan of jazz##1
9. the fan of dubstep is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | funk   | ambient      | hip-hop | folk  | dubstep   |
| Nationality   | indian | italian | russian | turkish   | japanese | brazilian |

