.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: salsa, gospel, funk, techno, reggae, d&b
The people use 6 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, roller, scooter, skateboard, motorbike
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
2. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is the fan of techno##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | techno | salsa      | gospel  | d&b | reggae |
| Transport     | jet-ski | motorbike  | skateboard | roller | scooter  | trike    |

