.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: photography, skydiving, writing, puzzles, video-games, drawing
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: indie, salsa, hip-hop, punk, metal, gospel
 1. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 3. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 5. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of punk##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | drawing | photography | video-games | skydiving | writing  |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | punk  | hip-hop  | indie | metal      | salsa |

