4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of electronic##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | techno  | disco     | country    | dubstep  | d&b          |
| Sport         | snowboarding  | skiing | cricket | parkour | baseball | soccer |

