4. the person driving the train is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | 7up | fanta | cola    | milk | lemonade      |
| Transport   | tram   | airplane     | helicopter      | taxi | train           | skateboard |

