.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: pineapple, orange, blueberry, cabbage, apple, asparagus
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: animation, romance, drama, fantasy, sports, spy
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1
3. the person watching romance movies is the person eating orange##1
4. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
6. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
7. the person eating asparagus is the person watching animation movies##1
8. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | orange | asparagus   | apple  | blueberry    | cabbage  | pineapple |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | animation | spy | sports | drama | fantasy |

