4. the architect is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the freelancer is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking sprite is the social-worker##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
9. the mechanic is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | sprite     | coffee | fanta | milk | soy-milk   |
| Job        | firefighter | social-worker | mechanic | architect   | doctor    | freelancer |

