.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-17::.
6 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, ferret, hedgehog, fish, frog
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: water-polo, climbing, tennis, cycling, rowing, basketball
1. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
9. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |    5    |       6       |
| Pet     | fish  | hedgehog       | frog   | guinea-pig      | ferret | goldfish          |
| Sport   | rowing | water-polo | tennis | climbing | cycling | basketball |

